<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.baseDesc>他曾经是一名获得勋章的 NCR 上校，如今却以冷酷无情的效率带领着逃兵，在荒地上开疆拓土。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.title>流氓上校</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.titleShort>上校</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.baseDesc>这位上校以其战场战术而闻名，因不服从命令而被流放，现在指挥着一支流氓军队。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.title>流亡战术家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.titleShort>战术家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.baseDesc>怀着建立新秩序的愿景，这位上校抛弃了 NCR，成为废土流放者中令人畏惧的军阀。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.title>废土军阀</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.titleShort>军阀</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.baseDesc>这位曾经受人尊敬的上校后来失宠，导致他聚集逃兵，在荒原上开辟了一条新道路。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.title>丢脸的领袖</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.titleShort>领导者</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.baseDesc>这位经验丰富、雄心勃勃的上校抛弃了指挥雇佣兵的方式，开创了自己的事业。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.title>雇佣兵指挥官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.titleShort>指挥官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.baseDesc>他曾经是一名 NCR 警官，利用自己的军衔谋取私利，直到他的罪行被发现。现在他在荒原上带领着逃兵。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.title>腐败中尉</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.titleShort>中尉</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.baseDesc>由于对 NCR 的领导不力感到沮丧，这名军官选择开小差，将自己的战术技能更好地运用到流氓队伍中。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.title>幻灭的战略家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.titleShort>战略家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.baseDesc>这位指挥官因质疑命令而被驱逐，现在带领逃兵与前盟友和敌人作战。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.title>流亡指挥官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.titleShort>指挥官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.baseDesc>这位擅长谈判的军官为了新派系的生存而放弃了斡旋交易和联盟。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.title>荒地外交官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.titleShort>外交官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.baseDesc>在向 NCR 复仇的驱使下，这位队长开小差，领导攻击他以前的战友并伸张正义。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.title>复仇队长</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.titleShort>队长</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.baseDesc>他曾经是一名忠诚的 NCR 士兵，但对无休止的竞选活动和腐败的军官感到厌倦。现在，他与逃兵同伴一起为生存而战。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.title>幻灭的步枪手</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.titleShort>步枪手</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.baseDesc>这位士兵在战斗中受伤并被指挥部遗弃，为了逃离一个不再关心自己的系统而逃亡。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.title>受伤的退伍军人</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.titleShort>老将</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.baseDesc>这位侦察兵擅长在荒地中航行，他离开了 NCR，利用自己的才能谋求自己的生存和利益。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.title>清道夫侦察兵</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.titleShort>侦察</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.baseDesc>怀揣着致富梦想，这位士兵放弃了 NCR，成为一名雇佣枪手，将自己的技能卖给出价最高的人。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.title>雇佣兵候选者</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.titleShort>有志者</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.baseDesc>Once tasked with protecting NCR assets, a single mistake led to disgrace and desertion.现在他在被遗弃的人中寻求救赎。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.title>耻辱的守卫</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.titleShort>警卫</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.titleShort>
</LanguageData>
